        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nPrevious version was a bit too aggressive in trying to simplify.  Because there was no way to list the deployments that we expect CM to make during the DCAE bootstrap, we could have seen incorrect healthcheck results if the bootstrap somehow hit an error early in its processing.\n\n(Lots of whitespace changes--sorry.)",
